OL,3,CPublic consultation on criminalising
OL,4,Cdeepfakes in N.Ireland
OL,6,FViews are being sought on proposals to
OL,7,Fcriminalise deepfake images of adults
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FStormont Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,11,Fdescribed such images as "abhorrent
OL,12,Fbehaviour which can have devastating
OL,13,Fconsequences".
OL,15,FA public consultation has been
OL,16,Flaunched on proposals to criminalise
OL,17,Fthe creation and sharing of sexually
OL,18,Fexplicit deepfake images of adults in
OL,19,Fan effort to protect the public from
OL,20,Fgrowing issues relating to the use of
OL,21,Fdeepfake technology.
