OL,4,Cdeepfakes in N.Ireland
OL,6,FMs Long said it is an issue that can
OL,7,Fruin lives. She said: "I am proposing
OL,8,Fto criminalise the increasingly
OL,9,Fprevalent and despicable behaviours of
OL,10,Fcreating and sharing sexually explicit
OL,11,Fdeepfake images, where somebody's
OL,12,Fimage is inserted into sexually
OL,13,Fexplicit content without their
OL,14,Fconsent," she said.
