OL,6,F"It is abhorrent behaviour which can
OL,7,Fhave devastating consequences for
OL,8,Fthose whose identities are misused,
OL,9,Fthe overwhelming majority of whom are
OL,10,Fwomen. "Victims report feeling
OL,11,Fembarrassed, humiliated, violated and
OL,12,Funsafe, they can suffer from anxiety
OL,13,Fand post-traumatic stress disorder,
OL,14,Fand some people even consider suicide
OL,15,Fbecause of their experiences.
OL,17,F"In short, this is an issue which can
OL,18,Fruin lives, which is why we are
OL,19,Fproposing to criminalise the creation
OL,20,Fand sharing of sexually explicit
OL,21,Fdeepfake images."
