OL,4,Cdeepfakes in N.Ireland
OL,6,FThe consultation includes
OL,7,Fconsideration of the sentences that
OL,8,Fshould be available to judges should
OL,9,Fthe creation and sharing of a sexually
OL,10,Fexplicit deepfake image become a
OL,11,Fcriminal offence.
OL,13,FMs Long said deepfake images are
OL,14,Fanother form of sexual abuse. "The
OL,15,Fcreation of these new offences will
OL,16,Fadd to a suite of measures already in
OL,17,Fplace to protect people from
OL,18,Fintolerable sexually motivated
OL,19,Fbehaviours and eradicate violence
OL,20,Fagainst women and girls," she said.
