OL,6,F"In 2022, I introduced a number of
OL,7,Foffences to deal with downblousing,
OL,8,Fupskirting and cyberflashing.
OL,9,F"Sexually explicit deepfake images are
OL,10,Fanother form of sexual abuse and
OL,11,Fexploitation. I will continue to react
OL,12,Fand respond to enhance legislation
OL,13,Frelating to those who misuse
OL,14,Fdevelopments in technology in such a
OL,15,Fway."
OL,17,FThe consultation will close on October
OL,18,F6, 2025.
